OL,4,CWater bills 'to fall in real terms'
OL,5, Household water bills in England and
OL,6, Wales will fall by between B#15 and
OL,7, B#25 a year from 2020 to 2025, the
OL,8, regulator Ofwat has pledged.
OL,10,FA forthcoming price review will give
OL,11,Fwater companies less room to charge
OL,12,Fcustomers based on the costs of raising
OL,13,Fdebt or equity, the regulator said.
OL,15,FOfwat was criticised by an influential
OL,16,Fgovernment committee in 2016 for
OL,17,Foverestimating water firms' costs.
OL,19,FThe companies are allowed to add the
OL,20,Fcost of inflation to bills.
